    public class HexavigesimalFormat
extends java.text.NumberFormat
    This formatter provides the conversion of a number to the Hexavigesmal value with the possibility of handling 26 unique values. An integer value 26 or above is reduce to Z
    Author:
    3M Health Information Systems for CMS Home Health
